    "• least-square regression (Catoni, 2004, Chapter 5) and robust variants (Audibert and Catoni, 2011; Catoni and Giulini, 2017).",
    "• sparse linear regression: Dalalyan and Tsybakov (2008) prove a rate of convergence similar to the one of the LASSO for the Gibbs posterior, under more general assumptions.",
    "Dalalyan and Tsybakov (2012), Alquier and Lounici (2011), and Dalalyan et al. (2018) provided many variants and improvements, see also Luu et al. (2019) for group-sparsity.",
    "• single-index regression, in small dimension (Gaïffas and Lecué, 2007), and in high-dimension, with sparsity (Alquier and Biau, 2013).",
    "• additive non-parametric regression (Guedj and Alquier, 2013)."
